				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/B%E1%BA%A3o-Ninh-S%C3%B9ng-Ph%C3%BAc-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-yadLYWXRS0UtV15FauZxIQ">Bảo Ninh Sùng Phúc tự bi - 保寧崇福寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/author-d8MSBkSrQsUgYbCqr0kX5g">Lý Thừa Ân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u-K%C3%ADnh-phi-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-brbq8Jm9uNrOLoqa5BIyuA">Điệu Kính phi kỳ 4 - 悼敬妃其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%C3%B4ng/author-J50Vl67kW8hllkOChILyMA">Nguyễn Hiển Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%C3%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-4-Ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-chu%E1%BB%B7-%C3%B4/poem-53ZjAXi8lSNpGs0f1TVm6g">Hoạ đáp thi kỳ 4 - Hoạ đại chuỷ ô - 和答詩其四－和大觜烏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Kh%E1%BB%91c-L%C6%B0u-t%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-5FspLDUtJbGzrhW9U-YDZQ">Khốc Lưu tư hộ kỳ 2 - 哭劉司戶其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/L%E1%BB%99-qu%C3%A1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-H%E1%BA%A3i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-ng%C5%A9-c%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-kzcEQT3mDPWAo5nViNxK_A">Lộ quá Bắc Ninh, Hải Dương tức sự hữu cảm ngũ cổ thập lục vận - 路過北寧海陽即事有感五古十六韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Ng%E1%BB%A5-c%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-Tu%E1%BB%87-vi%E1%BB%87n-chi-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-t%E1%BA%A1p-hoa-m%C3%A3n-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BB%AFu-h%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-w99oAsfudXJjoGO0C6_FbA">Ngụ cư Định Tuệ viện chi đông tạp hoa mãn sơn hữu hải đường - 寓居定慧院之東雜花滿山有海棠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%E1%BB%8Bch/Th%C3%A1i-li%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-6AfrtE9PzrytTnQ7LkKQaw">Thái liên khúc - 採蓮曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%E1%BB%8Bch/author-1Zi-jnBZOTtGhVGhP05YYQ">Tiêu Dịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-H%C6%B0ng-Nh%C3%A2n-L%C3%AA-do%C3%A3n-ph%C3%B3-khuy%E1%BA%BFt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-RkCRkHEnyIVv3fc6V81oag">Tiễn Hưng Nhân Lê doãn phó khuyết kỳ 1 - 餞興仁犁尹赴闕其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C3%A2n/Vu-s%C6%A1n-cao/poem-WnV1p4OPXVauG82TpQlA1Q">Vu sơn cao - 巫山高</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C3%A2n/author-iRSgb0bG9bw0C-4RvLUzdw">Phạm Vân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
